data.description: **10k SELLER CREDIT TOWARDS RATE BUY DOWN OR CLOSING COSTS**  Welcome to 1671 Brockton Ln, Beaumont, CA 92223 – a magnificent 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence offering an expansive 3,400 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space. Tankless water heater and four car tandem garage. Nestled in a prime location, this extraordinary property not only boasts stunning mountain views but also places you within a 15-minute drive of the picturesque Oak Glen orchards. It's ideally located near excellent schools, offers convenient freeway access, and is just a short drive to Cabazon Outlets and the excitement of Casino Morongo.
